snippet.title: Tiberian Sun Reborn Teaser
snippet.description:
Tiberian Sun Reborn is a game that brings Renegade and Tiberian Sun together into one package.

Fight for the Brotherhood of Nod or for the Global Defense Initiative while trying to avoid an ion storm.  Destroy the enemy base while trying to defend your own.

Download the game launcher at http://w3dhub.com
